Accessibility

- Alt tags have been given to all images on the site. This allows a description of the image in case the image doesn't load.

- Default font size in browsers is 16px which is the best for readability.
        - no font size has been changed.

- Limited the use of graphics to aid readability.

- Video has been embedded with close captions.

- Research carried out on the formatting of forms.
        - our form has made use of FieldSet and Legend to ensure elements are separated.
        - our form can be navigated using Tab and Arrow keys.

- Research indicated that black text on a white or pale background is best for readability.
        - background colour changed to alternative pale colour to aid the readability of articles which remain on white background

- font styling remains consistent with browser defaults - research suggests the defaults are best for readability for all.


